<doc id="1137548" wikidata="Q6685903" url="?curid=1137548" title="Loud Guitars, Big Suspicions">
<text>Loud Guitars, Big Suspicions is the debut album by American blues-rock artist Shannon Curfman, released in 1999 through Arista Records when she was 14 years old.

