* ⟨Sh⟩ (an English and Albanian digraph)
* Latin-script S-based digraphs (including the Italian ⟨sc⟩, English ⟨sh⟩, and Norwegian and Faroese ⟨sk⟩)
* Latin-script S-based trigraphs (including German ⟨sch⟩ and Italian ⟨sci⟩)

